<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><br />
<strong>SCP-CN-1364</strong>-欲加之惧</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sciencekiller" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5480202); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5480202&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609247507" alt="sciencekiller" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5480202)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sciencekiller" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5480202); return false;">sciencekiller</a></span>和<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rye-travis" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3290685); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3290685&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609247507" alt="Rye Travis" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3290685)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rye-travis" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3290685); return false;">Rye Travis</a></span></p>
<p><strong>鸣谢：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/onxy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3258233); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3258233&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609247507" alt="ONXY" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3258233)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/onxy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3258233); return false;">ONXY</a></span>，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/re-spectators" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3722555); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3722555&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609247507" alt="Re_spectators" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3722555)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/re-spectators" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3722555); return false;">Re_spectators</a></span>，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/enflowerz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4457426); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4457426&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609247507" alt="Enflowerz" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4457426)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/enflowerz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4457426); return false;">Enflowerz</a></span>，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-zhengshi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5288378); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5288378&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609247507" alt="Dr Zhengshi" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5288378)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-zhengshi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5288378); return false;">Dr Zhengshi</a></span>，readeiier，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ymq" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4337532); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4337532&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609247507" alt="YMQ" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4337532)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ymq" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4337532); return false;">YMQ</a></span>，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sistertan-greasy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3978938); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3978938&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609247507" alt="SisterTan_Greasy" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3978938)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sistertan-greasy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3978938); return false;">SisterTan_Greasy</a></span>，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tenth-lee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5226483); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5226483&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609247507" alt="Tenth Lee" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5226483)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tenth-lee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5226483); return false;">Tenth Lee</a></span>，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meltyland-nightmare" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6167306); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6167306&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609247507" alt="Meltyland Nightmare" style="background-image:url(http:/