<hr />
<p><strong>图片来源：</strong><br />
<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Univers_Fractal_J.H..jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Univers_Fractal_J.H..jpg</a><br />
<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Cultured_Rat_Hippocampal_Neuron_(24327909026).jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Cultured_Rat_Hippocampal_Neuron_(24327909026).jpg</a><br />
<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:DTI-sagittal-fibers.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:DTI-sagittal-fibers.jpg</a><br />
<a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/internetarchivebookimages/20370695282/">https://www.flickr.com/photos/internetarchivebookimages/20370695282/</a><br />
第一版Binah图标由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shineshadowd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3967806); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3967806&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609247507" alt="ShineShadowD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3967806)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shineshadowd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3967806); return false;">ShineShadowD</a></span>所作，第二版Binah由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3396110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609247507" alt="Kcorena" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3396110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;">Kcorena</a></span>所作<br />
第二迭代特遣队和铜印边疆协议logo由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3396110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609247507" alt="Kcorena" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3396110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;">Kcorena</a></span>所作<br />
第二迭代记录与信息安全管理部标志和应对协议题图来自<a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/desk-of-junior-designer-s-yvonne">此页面</a></p>
<p>其余图像由我所编辑。</p>
<hr />
<p><span style="font-family:'楷体';">多少年来我们才真正恐惧我们头上悬着的这把剑，在此之前我们没有低过头。</span></p>
</div>
